OL,3,CCampaigners call for hate crime
OL,4,Clegislation in Jersey
OL,6,FCampaigners are calling for specific
OL,7,Fhate crime legislation in Jersey in
OL,8,Flight of new figures.
OL,10,FIn data obtained exclusively by ITV
OL,11,FNews, reports of racially motivated
OL,12,Fhate crimes have more than doubled in
OL,13,FJersey since 2016.
OL,15,FThe total number of racially motivated
OL,16,Fhate crimes has risen from 21 to 44
OL,17,Fover the past nine years.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/7
