OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1777025179
OL,3,CCampaigners call for hate crime
OL,4,Clegislation in Jersey
OL,6,FIn 2016, seven incidents against
OL,7,Ffemale victims were reported to the
OL,8,Fpolice. By 2025, this rose to 20.
OL,9,FMeanwhile, for male victims, there
OL,10,Fwere 14 reports in 2016, which
OL,11,Fincreased to 24 last year.
OL,13,FLast summer, swastikas were sprayed
OL,14,Facross parts of St Helier, including
OL,15,Fon a primary school, leaving the
OL,16,FJewish community shaken.
OL,18,FIn addition to the swastikas,
OL,19,Fhomophobic graffiti was also painted
OL,20,Faround Jersey's capital.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/7
