OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1777025179
OL,3,CCampaigners call for hate crime
OL,4,Clegislation in Jersey
OL,6,FSpeaking about the incident, President
OL,7,Fof the Jersey Jewish Congregation,
OL,8,FMartha Berstein, told ITV News: "The
OL,9,Fsymbol itself is offensive for so many
OL,10,Freasons and here in Jersey, there's
OL,11,Fthe overlay of what happened during
OL,12,Fthe Occupation.
OL,14,F"I feel really threatened. I feel
OL,15,Freally anxious. Something that
OL,16,Fshouldn't have happened in Jersey had
OL,17,Fhappened."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
