CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1777025179
OL,3,CCampaigners call for hate crime
OL,4,Clegislation in Jersey
OL,6,FShe also said that recent attacks
OL,7,Fagainst Jewish communities in the UK,
OL,8,Fsuch as an arson attack on a Synagogue
OL,9,Fin London, were "almost inevitable"
OL,10,Fand have left members of Jersey's
OL,11,FJewish community on high alert.
OL,13,F"It's really heartbreaking, but many
OL,14,Fof us felt that (the attacks in the
OL,15,FUK) were almost inevitable - it's just
OL,16,Fbeen building and building up."
OL,26,@vD@QpmwD@Cpn
