CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1777025179
OL,3,CCampaigners call for hate crime
OL,4,Clegislation in Jersey
OL,6,FKaye Nicholson, CEO of Liberate
OL,7,FJersey, believes that a hate crime law
OL,8,Fon the island would help to "send a
OL,9,Fmessage to the world about the kind of
OL,10,Fjurisdiction Jersey is".
OL,12,FShe continued: "It also sends a
OL,13,Fmessage to our local community that
OL,14,Fthis behaviour is not tolerated, that
OL,15,Fthere is recourse for people who find
OL,16,Fthemselves victims of these kinds of
OL,17,Fcrimes to follow through with that.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1777025179
OL,3,CCampaigners call for hate crime
OL,4,Clegislation in Jersey
OL,6,F"We need some clarity about how people
OL,7,Fgo about reporting, how police look at
OL,8,Fthose types of crimes, and then we
OL,9,Fwould like to see explicit hate crime
OL,10,Flegislation brought forward."
OL,12,FCraig Jackson, Acting Superintendent
OL,13,Fat the States of Jersey Police, said:
OL,14,F"Hate crime is not tolerated, and it
OL,15,Fis underreported - anyone who is
OL,16,Finvolved in a crime or incident that
OL,17,Fis hate-related should report it to
OL,18,Fthe police.
OL,20,F"This will help to secure the evidence
OL,21,Fand bring those offenders to justice".
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/7
